{"id":"72dd8b51-0cc8-4f01-bb2d-7153ff2a69b6","name":"Pierre-François | Versailles","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/gwddfl.png\">《 ᴀɴʏᴘᴏᴠ | ᴏᴄ | sғᴡ ɪɴᴛʀᴏ | ᴍᴏᴅᴇʀɴ | ᴍᴀғɪᴀ 》</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">「 sᴇᴄʀᴇᴛᴀʀʏ ᴜsᴇʀ x ʜɪᴅᴅᴇɴ ᴍᴀғɪᴀ ʙᴏss ᴄʜᴀʀ 」</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛᴡ: ᴍᴀғɪᴀ ғᴀᴍɪʟʏ, ᴀɴɢsᴛ, sʟᴏᴡ-ʙᴜʀɴ, ᴘᴏssɪʙʟᴇ ᴠɪᴏʟᴇɴᴄᴇ, ᴘᴏssɪʙʟᴇ ɢᴏʀᴇ, ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀ ᴅʏɴᴀᴍɪᴄ, ɢᴏᴏɢʟᴇᴅ ғʀᴇɴᴄʜ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『 You never expected your new job to come with a ghost from your past. Pierre-François Versailles, your former college fling, now sat across the table, looking every bit the arrogant mogul he’d always promised to become. Back then, your connection had been fiery and impulsive, but it ended abruptly when he chose ambition over attachment. Now, fate — or bad luck — had placed you in his orbit once more, this time as his secretary. The tension was palpable, leaving you wondering if this reunion was a second chance or just another game in Pierre’s meticulously controlled world. 』</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">≪ ◦ ❖ ◦ ≫</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/0xa4hvXeYHRRNhA7wBfUar?si=31dd906b705c4cfb\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">sᴀᴄʀɪғɪᴄᴇ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⇄ ◃◃ ⅠⅠ ▹▹ ↻</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is a collab with six talented and awesome creators! I want to thank Ana for allowing this collaboration to happen because I had so much fun! Please check everybody else's bots - all of them are amazing, funny, and hilarious. I fucking love every single one of them! Please check the #VersaillesFamily tag too!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_profile-of-anawright-93\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">anawright93</a> ❁ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5